{"word":"G230 - ἀληθῶς - alēthōs - al-ay-thoce' - Indeed","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀληθῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">alēthōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">al-ay-thoce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Indeed</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மெய்யாய், நிச்சயமாய், மெய்யாகவே, உத்தம - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"truly, of a truth, in reality; most certainly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G227 - ἀληθής - alēthḗs - al-ay-thace'/227\">G227</a>; <i>truly:</i> - indeed, surely, of a surety, truly, of a (in) truth, verily, very.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}